Description: Two original tinted lithographs; (1) "Tyre from the Isthmus"; sand dunes and ruins in foreground, city in distance, title beneath (plate 71); (2) "Sidon"; beach scene, city in distance, title beneath (plate 73), both signed by David Roberts; label entitled "David Roberts, The Holy Land, Syria, Idumea, Arabia, Egypt and Nubia (1855-6)", cream mount and plastic cover.
Acquisition name: Donated by: Dr St John Simpson
